The icons inside this folder are adapted from the IBM Carbon design system.
For the original source, see:
https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon

The following files are unmodified except for a change in file type:
  CarbonDataPlayer.png
  CarbonPageScroll.png
  CarbonPause.png
  CarbonPlay.png
  CarbonArrowLeft.png
  CarbonArrowRight.png
  CarbonChartLine.png

The following files are derivatives based on the work of IBM Corp:
  ASESkipBack.png
  ASESkipForward.png
